ign: center;\">4</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">6</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">1</td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\">4ᵗʰ</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">+2</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">@UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.izdnt7eqytkwgb1d]{Ability Score Improvement} @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.88pcGHmEKZru59w9]{Second Flame}</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">2ⁿᵈ</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">4</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">8</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">1</td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\">5ᵗʰ</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">+3</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">@UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-feats.Item.zImenvwYzk3mzIjX]{Knight of Fire}</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">3ʳᵈ</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">5</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">10</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">1</td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\">6ᵗʰ</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">+3</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">@UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.d4tvwfIOmRlzwDMi]{Flameborne Reputation}</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">3ʳᵈ</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">5</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">11</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">2</td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\">7ᵗʰ</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">+3</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">@UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.RR9TvEeTw2Qacrck]{Unique Flame} @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.ctqkypKl57yFW1UW]{Ashen Aura}</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">4ᵗʰ</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">6</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">12</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">2</td></tr><tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\">8ᵗʰ</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">+3</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">@UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.izdnt7eqytkwgb1d]{Ability Score Improvement} @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.smRj2SRhD6HdeG1z]{Lord of Fire}</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">4ᵗʰ</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">6</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">13</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">2</td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><h3>Hit Points</h3><p><strong>Hit Dice:</strong> 1d8 per fire lord level</p><p><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level:</strong> 8 + your Constitution modifier</p><p><strong>Hit Points at Higher Levels:</strong> 1d8 (or 5) + your Constitution modifier per fire lord level after 1st</p><p></p><h2>Proficiencies</h2><p><strong>Armor:</strong> light armor, medium armor</p><p><strong>Weapons:</strong> simple weapons, martial weapons</p><p><strong>Tools:</strong> smithing tools</p><p><strong>Saving Throws:</strong> Constitution, Charisma</p><p><strong>Skills:</strong> Choose two from Athletics, Deception, Intimidation, Insight, Perception, Persuasion, Religion</p><p></p><h2>Equipment</h2><p>You begin the game with 150 gold, which you can spend on your character’s starting weapons, armor, and adventuring gear. Also consult the Suggested Equipment section of your chosen background.</p>",
